斯体育场展览“下班后黎明”北美巡回演出</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1240" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Weeknd-announces-second-Las-Vegas-stadium-show-for-‘After-Hours-Til-Dawn-North-American-tour.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Weeknd。信用 - 凯文·冬天" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Weeknd-announces-second-Las-Vegas-stadium-show-for-‘After-Hours-Til-Dawn-North-American-tour.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Weeknd-announces-second-Las-Vegas-stadium-show-for-‘After-Hours-Til-Dawn-North-American-tour-400x248.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Weeknd-announces-second-Las-Vegas-stadium-show-for-‘After-Hours-Til-Dawn-North-American-tour-800x496.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Weeknd-announces-second-Las-Vegas-stadium-show-for-‘After-Hours-Til-Dawn-North-American-tour-696x432.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Weeknd-announces-second-Las-Vegas-stadium-show-for-‘After-Hours-Til-Dawn-North-American-tour-1392x863.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The-Weeknd-announces-second-Las-Vegas-stadium-show-for-‘After-Hours-Til-Dawn-North-American-tour-1068x662.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>由于对门票的需求很高， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-weeknd">Weeknd</a>宣布了第二次拉斯维加斯体育场展览“下班后”北美巡回演出。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-weeknd-hurry-up-tomorrow-review-3833573">周末 - “明天快点”评论：体育场填补超级巨星准备继续前进</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-announces-after-hours-til-dawn-2025-north-american-tour-3833671">一月份</a>，音乐家分享了一次大规模北美巡回演出的细节，该巡回赛于今年晚些时候在体育场举行。这次旅行将于2025年5月至9月在休斯敦，纳什维尔，芝加哥，温哥华和亚特兰大等城市停留。</p><p> Weeknd定于7月5日在拉斯维加斯效力；但是，由于需求量很高，在7月4日向拉斯维加斯添加了额外的演出。</p><p>这位歌手长期以来的专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-weeknd-hurry-up-tomorrow-review-3833573">“ Purrin Up明天”</a>发行之后，巡回新闻发布了。记录标志着歌手的“黎明FM”三部曲的第三章也是最后一章，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-delays-new-album-hurry-up-tomorrow-due-to-los-angeles-wildfires-3828567">在上周被推迟后今天到达。</a></p><p> Weeknd（真名Abel Tesfaye）将播放“ Purrine tearly tearly”， <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-weeknd-after-hours-review-his-most-all-encompassing-record-to-date-is-also-an-existential-quandary-2632591">“下班后”</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-weeknd-dawn-fm-review-3132463">“ Dawn FM”</a>的新歌，以及他目录的其余部分中的命中。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/playboi-carti">Playboi Carti</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mike-dean">Mike Dean</a>都将加入歌手，担任特别嘉宾。在这次旅行中，《周末》已经与<a href="https://www.globalcitizen.org/en/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">全球公民</a>合作，每张售出的每张门票的1美元都将捐赠，以支持来自世界各地脆弱社区的儿童。<a href="https://www.globalcitizen.org/en/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>了解有关慈善机构的更多信息，然后<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fthe-weeknd-tickets%2Fartist%2F1697014" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问这里</a>购买门票。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DFfoRneuJ2D/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; w