ts/Dua-Lipa">Dua Lipa</a>的露面。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/jennie-blackpink-ruby-review-3844348">珍妮 - “露比”评论：一个大胆，自我保证的处女作，重新定义了她的叙述</a></strong></li></ul><p>今天（3月10日）发行的“车把”是珍妮首张个人专辑“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/jennie-blackpink-ruby-review-3844348">Ruby</a> ”的第五首单曲。这首歌是由Lipa，Rob Bisel，Amy Allen，Brittany Amaradio和James Ghaleb共同撰写的。</p><p>音乐视频由BRTHR导演，开头是K-pop歌手的镜头，躺在一张圆形床上，穿着报纸印花合奏，周围有电视屏幕。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Jennie＆Dua Lipa-车把（官方视频）" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/seARsMwjbEU?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>然后看到她在一条多雨的小巷里走路，咬着手指，导致雨水停在位。 “我恋爱和坠入爱河 /就像星期二的醉汉 /我总是全力以赴，全力以赴 /在车把上 /在地面上如此艰难 /如果我一个人，堕落，堕落，堕落&#39;，堕落&#39;，我们不是要谈论这一点，”她站在一个轻声的舞蹈上时唱歌。</p><p>然后，Lipa以射击星的身份出现，并穿着透明的雨衣，下面有闪闪发光的连衣裙。视频看到两位歌手在工作室里跳舞和唱歌，同时躺在闪闪发光的心形蜘蛛网上。视频以烟花爆炸而结束。</p><p>除了“车把”之外，詹妮（Jennie）的LP“ Ruby”还包括单曲“<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blackpink-jennie-music-video-like-jennie-3844343">像Jennie</a> ”， <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/track/jennie-mantra-track-review-blackpink-3801776">“ Mantra”</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blackpink-jennie-love-hangover-featuring-dominic-fike-3833433">“ Love Handover”，其中包括Dominic Fike</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blackpink-jennie-surprise-music-video-new-single-zen-3832135">“ Zen”</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blackpinks-jennie-teases-new-single-extral-featuring-doechii-3837935">Doechii的“ Zen”以及“ Extracl”</a> 。其他关于“ Ruby”的合作者包括“车把”上的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">Dua Lipa</a> ，fkj on&#39;Intro：Jane&#39;，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/childish-gambino">幼稚的Gambino</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kali-uchis">Kali Uchis</a>在“该死的正确”上。</p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/jennie-blackpink-ruby-review-3844348">对“ Ruby”的四星级评论</a>中， <em>NME</em>分享了：“经过多年的约会生活，从约会生活到面部表情的所有事物，珍妮用“ Ruby”将镜头倒在自己身上，在那里她以惊人的清晰度抓住了自己对自己的神话的控制。她断言自己不仅是全球明星，而且是作为一位完全实现的艺术家，以意义上的意图塑造了自己的声音和视野。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DG3M6Thv12F/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,6